<link>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/17/vercel-releases-eve/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.marktechpost.com/?p=80581</guid>
<pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 17:22:51 +0000</pubDate>
<source>marktechpost.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【marktechpost.com】Vercel 已开源 Eve，这是一个 Apache-2.0 许可的智能体框架，目前处于公开预览阶段。每个智能体对应一个文件目录，内置持久化执行、沙箱、审批、连接、频道和评估功能。可通过 npx eve@latest init 进行脚手架搭建，并通过 vercel deploy 直接部署而无需修改。本文《Vercel Releases Eve: An Open-Source AI Agent Framework Where Each Agent is a Directory of Files Mapped to Capabilities》最初发表于 MarkTechPost。<br/><br/><a href="https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/17/vercel-releases-eve/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
